# Dotfiles: ignore everything, allowlist tracked files
# With showUntrackedFiles=no, untracked files won't show in status.
# This file prevents accidental `git add` of things you don't want.

# ── Ignore everything by default ──
*

# ── Shell ──
!.zshrc
!.zshenv
!.p10k.zsh

# ── Git ──
!.gitconfig
!.cfg-ignore

# ── Tool configs ──
!.config/
!.config/mise/
!.config/mise/config.toml
!RectangleConfig.json

# ── Claude Code ──
# Must un-ignore parent dirs first, then contents
!.claude/
!.claude/CLAUDE.md
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/agents/**
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/commands/**
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/hooks/**
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**
!.claude/siraj-experiments/
!.claude/siraj-experiments/**

# ── Docs ──
!README.md
